Package: hexmakR
Title: Interactive Hex Sticker Generator for R Packages
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Raban", "Heller", , "raban.heller@uni-ulm.de", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-8006-9742"))
Description: Create publication-ready hexagon stickers for R packages
    interactively via a Shiny app or programmatically via R functions.
    Complements the 'hexSticker' package (which embeds R plots into
    stickers) by providing an interactive visual designer with 19 curated
    color themes (dark and light variants), 46 built-in scientific and
    technical icons, custom image upload support, font selection, and
    export to transparent PNG. Designed for the R package ecosystem with
    presets for CRAN, Bioconductor, Tidyverse, and domain-specific
    color palettes.
